TITLE: Advanced Call Queue with ID Tracking
DESCRIPTION: More sophisticated implementation using call IDs to track and manage the queue state, handling multiple calls more effectively.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dubzzz/fast-check/blob/main/website/docs/tutorials/detect-race-conditions/wrapping-up.mdx#2025-04-11_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
let callId = 0;
let previous = undefined;
function fireCall(call) {
  const currentCallId = ++callId;
  const next = previous === undefined ? call() : previous.then(() => call());
  previous = next.then(() => {
    if (callId === currentCallId) {
      previous = undefined;
    }
  });
}
```

