TITLE: Naive First-Call Optimization
DESCRIPTION: Initial attempt to optimize the first call execution while maintaining queue behavior for subsequent calls.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dubzzz/fast-check/blob/main/website/docs/tutorials/detect-race-conditions/wrapping-up.mdx#2025-04-11_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
let previous = undefined;
function fireCall(call) {
  if (previous === undefined) {
    previous = call();
  } else {
    previous = previous.then(() => call());
  }
}
```

