TITLE: Generating Double Precision Floats with fast-check
DESCRIPTION: Functions for generating double precision floating point numbers with configurable ranges and constraints using fc.double(). Supports infinity, NaN, and exclusion options.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dubzzz/fast-check/blob/main/website/docs/core-blocks/arbitraries/primitives/number.md#2025-04-11_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
