TITLE: Initial Linear Search Implementation in mapToConstant
DESCRIPTION: The original linear search implementation in mapToConstant that caused performance issues with larger entry arrays. This approach had O(n) complexity for each lookup.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dubzzz/fast-check/blob/main/website/blog/2024-11-05-whats-new-in-fast-check-3-23-0/index.md#2025-04-11_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
function buildForChoiceIndex(choiceIndex: number) {
  let idx = -1;
  let numSkips = 0;
  while (choiceIndex >= numSkips) {
    numSkips += entries[++idx].num;
  }
  return entries[idx].build(choiceIndex - numSkips + entries[idx].num);
}
```

